In [26]:
populations <- c("pbmc", "T", "B", "Mono")
In [27]:
for (i in populations){
    x1 <- get(paste0(i,".expression.immediate"))
    x2 <- get(paste0(i,".expression.longterm"))
    
    x3 <- x1[,2:7]
    x4 <- x2[,2:7]
    
    
    row.names(x3) <- x1$X
    row.names(x4) <- x2$X
    
    colnames(x3) <- c("L-92", "L-44", "L-3", "R+1", "R+45", "R+82")
    colnames(x4) <- c("L-92", "L-44", "L-3", "R+1", "R+45", "R+82")
    
    assign(paste0(i,".expression.immediate"), x3)
    assign(paste0(i,".expression.longterm"), x4)
}

In [32]:
for (i in populations){
    x1 <- get(paste0(i,".expression.immediate"))
    x2 <- get(paste0(i,".expression.longterm"))
    
    x1$Preflight <- (x1$June.2021+x1$August.2021+x1$September.Pre.launch)/3
    x2$Preflight <- (x2$June.2021+x2$August.2021+x2$September.Pre.launch)/3
    
    x3 <- x1 %>% select(Preflight, September.Post.launch, November.2021, December.2021)
    x4 <- x2 %>% select(Preflight, September.Post.launch, November.2021, December.2021)
    
    
    row.names(x3) <- x1$X
    row.names(x4) <- x2$X
    
    colnames(x3) <- c("Pre-flight", "R+1", "R+45", "R+82")
    colnames(x4) <- c("Pre-flight", "R+1", "R+45", "R+82")
    
    assign(paste0(i,".expression.immediate.3"), x3)
    assign(paste0(i,".expression.longterm.3"), x4)
}

In [73]:
save_pheatmap_tiff_2 <- function(x, filename, width=10000, height=3000, res = 300) {
  tiff(filename, width = width, height = height, res = res, compression = "lzw")
  grid::grid.newpage()
  grid::grid.draw(x$gtable)
  dev.off()
}

for (i in populations){
    x1 <- get(paste0(i, ".expression.immediate.3"))

    options(repr.plot.width=40, repr.plot.height=10)
    
    a1 <- pheatmap::pheatmap(t(as.matrix(x3)), 
                   color = colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(n = 10, name = "RdGy")))(100), 
                   cluster_cols = T, cluster_rows = F, 
                   legend = TRUE,
                             cellwidth=2,
                             cellheight=20,
                   annotation_row=anno_row2,
                             
                   annotation_colors = list(Timepoint = c("Pre-flight"="#377EB8", "Immediately Post-flight" = "#E41A1C", 
                                                         "Long-term Post-flight" = "#D9742C")),
                   
                   scale="column",
                             
                   show_colnames = F, show_rownames = T)
    
    save_pheatmap_tiff_2(a1, paste0("output/update/", i, ".deg.immediate.heatmap2.tiff"))
